About
=======

This library contains base classes for Maven Mojos that need to run in a modified classloader.

AbstractClassLoaderSwappingMojo: common logic for replacing/restoring context classloader in a Mojo.
BuildClassPathMojo: base class for Maven Mojos that load classes from the compile classpath.

